    Page: 135
    Verse: 13
Tags:
  - Evil
---
There is a great difference between resisting the negative force and
renouncing it. When you resist this dark force, or what man calls evil, you
give the subject attention and growth. When you renounce evil you take your
attention from it and give your attention to what you want.
